---
title: Chicken Almond Milanese with Roasted Sweet Potato Wedges and Broccoli
description: Milanesa is a cooking technique common in South American countries where thin pieces of meat are breaded and cooked. Japanese-style panko breadcrumbs is what gives this chicken the signature crispy coating!
